org.smartclean

Interface SCSDKClientInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DeviceMgmtSDKInterface, GridsSDKInterface, MetricsSDKInterface, SCTeamsPropSDKInterface, WFMSDKInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SCSDKMasterService

    public interface SCSDKClientInterface
extends WFMSDKInterface, MetricsSDKInterface, GridsSDKInterface, DeviceMgmtSDKInterface, SCTeamsPropSDKInterface
    This is the master interface class which extends the internal interfaces of individual modules to expose module-wise defined functions made available to the client.
